{
  "stem": "311.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you put the green color on it, it's without paint, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some kind of chemicals he used and fire to get-- to get the colors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the secrets, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every-- every trade had a secret, and he was one of the-- one of the best.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every trade was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they were-- the rest was mostly farmers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the trades were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the-- all the maker-- all that was mechanics, all that was making leather, you know, leather goods or garments or-- you know, the whole-- the-- the whole industry.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- there was very few factories, you know, Polish factories around Krakow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even those big ones, they were partly Jewish, you know, like the nail factories and--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one in Krakow?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were-- they were merchants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were doing-- no, they were everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, you know, outside, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Krakow was combined.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- happens to be-- this was already the big city with 240,000 people, which I understand now it's got a million people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and all mostly surrounded with farmland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you know, the farmland-- now, the farmers used to come in to sell the products and to buy-- to spend their money at the stores, mostly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Especially, they used to come to the Jewish quarters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They could-- they got a better deal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a-- we had a shop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did some stamping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did-- it-- it was a-- the company name was Metalosport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did sport items, and we did some-- most of it, it was jewelry for horses for-- for the bridals.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a good-- it was an item, I never saw it in the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
